title: Narrative

* This example shows a simple table of contents with 3 levels
* The "root" elements are ''tagged Contents''
* The tiddler [[aa-aa]] contains a field: `caption: aa-aa -> cc`, which is shown as the link text
* The [[aa-aa]] tiddler contains a field: `target: cc` so clicking the link opens the ''cc'' tiddler instead of `aa-aa`

{{example-overview}}

